ties of restrictedProgram item, instead of hardcoding it: </p>  <pre><code>foreach($installedProgram in $installedPrograms)     {         foreach($restrictedProgram in $restrictedPrograms)         {             // Foreach property in $restrictedProgram, compare it with the corresponding property in $installedProgram ??         }     } </code></pre>